See docs/user/clambc-user.pdf, chapter 1 "Installation".
Quick start for building:
-------------------------
mkdir obj
cd obj
../llvm/configure --enable-optimized --enable-targets=host-only
--disable-bindings --prefix=/usr/local/clamav
(ulimit -t 3600 -v 512000; make clambc-only -j4)
(ulimit -t 3600 -v 512000; make install-clambc -j8)

For building and running tests:
------------------------------
mkdir obj
cd obj
../llvm/configure --enable-optimized --enable-targets=host-only
--disable-bindings --prefix=/usr/local/clamav
(ulimit -t 3600 -v 512000; make clambc-only -j4)
make -j4
make check-all

See docs/user/clambc-user.pdf, section "1.3 Building" if build fails.
